data.oai_dc:dc: The checklist is supplied for the Catalogue of Life by FADA project. FADA, the Freshwater Animal Diversity Assessment is an informal network of scientists specialized in freshwater biodiversity. FADA contributes freshwater taxa in the CoL proto-GSD. Kotov, A., Forró, L., Korovchinsky, N.M. and A. Petrusek, 2013 Jan 25, World checklist of freshwater Cladocera species. World Wide Web electronic publication. Available online at http://fada.biodiversity.be/group/show/17 [date accessed]
